{"id": 1166, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得现在的电视剧都不走心到什么地步了？", "description": "还是觉得编剧和剧务应该多做功课，别把都市剧拍成情景喜剧，（题图来自：Ana Albero）", "record_count": 8574, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160810211624WIkbrlcyqsFLZxNU.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-12T17:00:03Z", "options": [{"id": 107264, "content": "看电视主要剧情不看，找哪里好笑，值得吐槽，后来都不想吐槽了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696088}, {"id": 111872, "content": "手撕鬼子\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739592}, {"id": 107265, "content": "让人觉得演员演的不自然", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708195}, {"id": 107777, "content": "尤其芒果台的剧不收音配音超奇怪", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685215}, {"id": 107778, "content": "只有一起经历了革命和抗日的爱情才最浪漫", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573600}, {"id": 107779, "content": "反派脑残到了一定的地步，关键是主角也把反派当成了脑残", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715501}, {"id": 107524, "content": "出来一句台词观众都知道下一句要说什么了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714588}, {"id": 108036, "content": "只玩套路，不动脑子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717322}, {"id": 107270, "content": "打架时死法都是一样的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670944}, {"id": 107526, "content": "敌方毫无理由的强大，毫无预见的出现只因为主角需要些苦难，然后毫无理由的就败了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670054}, {"id": 165383, "content": "国产剧现在基本不看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857330}, {"id": 107271, "content": "抗日神剧，手撕鬼子，裤裆藏手雷", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341380}, {"id": 107272, "content": "“我们的狙击手，八百里外一枪一个”", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404446}, {"id": 107528, "content": "韩国电视剧里的大龄剩女，到了中国就变成了宋丹丹年龄级的阿姨", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700082}, {"id": 107273, "content": "万年不变剧情，没有新意，抗日剧里的各种神技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59704}, {"id": 107274, "content": "国产剧不收音配音极度浮夸", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653104}, {"id": 107275, "content": "編劇是不是都用機器人模式的？給點腦力運動觀眾可以嗎？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 503849}, {"id": 107276, "content": "都是小说改编，有些小说只能适合阅读偏偏改编电视剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713873}, {"id": 107532, "content": "中文差到沦丧的地步，写台词的都是初中文化", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 107788, "content": "古装剧的服装颜色和看上去的质感都特别浮夸，没有一点古典的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715620}, {"id": 107277, "content": "逻辑永远没童话故事严谨，特效永远没动画片精致。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639381}, {"id": 107533, "content": "消音连背景音乐一起不见了，录音棚的音色一听就听出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714505}, {"id": 107278, "content": "直接翻拍小说 一直重复老梗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462071}, {"id": 107279, "content": "替他们尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595556}, {"id": 107280, "content": "好多演员只有颜没有技，让人分分钟跳戏，满满的尴尬…还不如去看小说…", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313885}, {"id": 107792, "content": "一个题材的电视剧火了以后，山寨版便不断出现", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224557}, {"id": 107281, "content": "看片头曲就知道结局，看第一集可以知道谁和谁在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713887}, {"id": 107537, "content": "演技烂剧情狗血全靠颜值，有时候颜值也挑不起大梁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711274}, {"id": 107282, "content": "所谓的演技就是“瞪眼大吼发牢骚”", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 108818, "content": "强行卖腐看的心累（虽然我是腐女）?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723023}, {"id": 107283, "content": "内容硬伤，编剧一次又一次刷新TA心中观众的智商下限。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 392593}, {"id": 108051, "content": "不看电视的飘过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642016}, {"id": 109331, "content": "打开电视满满都是古装，抗日，能不能有点科幻前卫点题材的电视剧？现代剧末剧情也各种不符合逻辑，能不能带脑子拍电视剧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725262}, {"id": 107284, "content": "那几个主演换套衣服，换个场景继续谈恋爱，就有了都市剧，抗战剧，穿越剧....", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713876}, {"id": 107798, "content": "玛丽苏到吐血。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623394}, {"id": 108822, "content": "电视剧看几集就知道它的套路，发生什么事我都知道结局如何", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723069}, {"id": 107287, "content": "都市剧里个个都用苹果手机，出几代就用几代，替别人打广告，韩国剧里各个角色用的永远是三星，这就是差距", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692328}, {"id": 107288, "content": "把古装剧当现代片来拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713901}, {"id": 107289, "content": "是电视剧呢，还是动画片。整个智商都下降了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698712}, {"id": 107290, "content": "盔甲像塑料壳，华丽丽的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141957}, {"id": 107291, "content": "特定的某个桥段我真的可以猜到他们接下来要说什么做什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692328}, {"id": 107292, "content": "女主角的穿衣风格越来越俗，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692328}, {"id": 107294, "content": "无视观众的智商 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682076}, {"id": 107296, "content": "逻辑混乱，剧情老套，结局显而易见，编剧、导演振振有词：没错，观众都是傻子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441430}, {"id": 107297, "content": "不管那个电视剧，看了第一集后就猜到结局，然后就不想看了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713913}, {"id": 107553, "content": "尤其国产片 越来越没意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714713}, {"id": 107298, "content": "阿猫阿狗都是霸道总裁", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 107554, "content": "除了谈恋爱 没有别的可讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714713}, {"id": 107300, "content": "中文对英文交流?", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709589}, {"id": 107301, "content": "主角永远不死  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709379}]}